@node "History" "History"
 @{b}39.3 (13.6.95) 4660 bytes
 =========================@{ub}

 · Removed support for all tooltypes except EXTRAINFOCMD, as ExtraWBInfo
   now makes use of ExtraInfos READICON argument.

 @{b}39.2 (10.6.95) 5380 bytes
